2026-04-15T05:39:29.658Z JOY-00E8-3D comment.added "Plan: ADR-033 drafted in JI repo at docs/dev/architecture/decisions/ADR-033-per-session-human-authorization.md. Implementation will land JOY-00E8-3D and JOY-00E9-C2 together as one coordinated migration (shared project.yaml schema change, shared auth/token/session code paths). JOY-00EA-45 (single-use + 2h TTL) lands separately on top. JOY-00EB-6C (shell completion) is independent." [ai:claude@joy delegated-by:horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
